WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:11.560
Dominoes, Quick Starter, Merlin, by Janet Hardy Gould, Read by Jenny Bryce, Joanna Hall,

00:11.560 --> 00:21.000
Roger May, Christopher Mills, Paul Panting, and James Daniel Wilson, published and copyright

00:21.000 --> 00:25.840
Oxford University Press 2014.

00:25.840 --> 00:54.320
Number One, The Boy Merlin, Young Merlin lives in a castle with his mother, Princess

00:54.320 --> 01:05.960
Adam. The castle is in Wales, in the west of King Vortigern's Kingdom. Merlin doesn't

01:05.960 --> 01:18.720
know his father. He's fighting for the king far away. The castle is near a forest. Merlin

01:19.040 --> 01:29.640
and his mother often walk there. She teaches him about forest plants. When you're older,

01:29.640 --> 01:39.360
you can come here without me, she says, but be careful. There are many hunters and an

01:39.440 --> 01:53.400
enchantress, Keridwen, lives here too. Merlin's only friend is a toad. One day Merlin visits

01:53.400 --> 02:06.120
the village near the castle. Two boys, Morfran and Arwell are behind him, but Merlin doesn't

02:06.120 --> 02:21.040
see them. He talks to his toad. Merlin's talking to his toad. Morfran laughs. Go away.

02:21.040 --> 02:29.240
Merlin says, or when my father comes back home, we're not afraid Merlin. Your father's never

02:29.240 --> 02:41.160
at home. Arwell says, and is he truly your father? Perhaps you're a demon's child. That

02:41.160 --> 02:50.600
night, Merlin tells his mother everything. What can I do about these boys? He asks.

03:00.120 --> 03:04.520
Chapter Two, the bullies come back.

03:04.520 --> 03:32.200
I can talk to those bullies. Princess Adan says, no. Merlin answers. They call me a mother's

03:32.280 --> 03:42.720
boy without that. Then your father can speak to them after he comes home. She smiles. But

03:42.720 --> 03:57.000
be careful with Morfran. He's Keridwen's son. Next week, Merlin goes to the village shop

03:57.000 --> 04:09.520
with his mother. He sits near the door with his toad in his hand. Suddenly, Morfran and

04:09.520 --> 04:23.960
Arwell clump out in front of him. It's Merlin and his toad. They cry. The toad is afraid.

04:23.960 --> 04:38.480
It falls to the ground. Let's see your toad jump. Morfran laughs. He runs after it. When

04:38.560 --> 04:51.600
Merlin's mother arrives, the bullies leave. That night, Merlin sees his father in a dream.

04:53.760 --> 05:05.840
He is sitting under an oak tree after a fight with the king's enemies. I'm dying. Merlin's father

05:05.840 --> 05:17.440
tells him. Father, no. I need your help with some bullies. Merlin cries. When they bully you,

05:18.480 --> 05:28.320
walk away. His father says, look for the biggest oak in the forest. There's something important near

05:28.320 --> 05:42.720
it. Next morning, Merlin tells his mother about the dream. Listen to your father. She says quietly.

05:45.600 --> 05:58.080
When Merlin meets the bullies again, they take his toad. Say goodbye to Mr toad. Morfran laughs.

05:58.800 --> 06:14.240
Merlin remembers his dream and walks into the forest. He lives there for days and eats forest plants.

06:16.480 --> 06:27.680
Then one day he finds the biggest oak in the forest. There's a little house near it.

06:29.280 --> 06:44.080
In front of the house, there's a boy. He's sitting near a cauldron. Who's that? Merlin thinks.

06:44.080 --> 06:55.920
Chapter 4. Merlin runs away.

07:14.080 --> 07:27.760
Come here, boy. The enchantress cries. I need to run. Merlin thinks. In his head, he sees a hair.

07:29.440 --> 07:42.960
Then suddenly he is a hair. Aha. He thinks. So now I can change into different animals.

07:44.880 --> 07:57.120
Merlin runs away into the forest. I can easily run faster than Caridwin now. He thinks.

07:59.360 --> 08:12.480
But when he looks behind him, he sees a big dog. It is running after him and its angry mouse is

08:12.560 --> 08:21.520
open. Oh no! He thinks. Caridwin can change into different animals too.

08:24.320 --> 08:36.880
Merlin moves quickly through the trees. But he can hear Caridwin behind him. She is coming nearer.

08:37.760 --> 08:54.560
Just then, he arrives at a lake. I need to be a fish. He thinks. Suddenly, he's a long, dark fish.

08:56.320 --> 09:06.560
He moves fast through the cold water of the lake. I'm all right now. He thinks.

09:07.680 --> 09:19.600
But when he looks back, an otter is coming through the water behind him. Caridwin's an otter now.

09:20.560 --> 09:32.160
He thinks. So he changes into a little bird and goes far up into the sky.

09:33.040 --> 09:48.080
But soon, he hears an angry cry behind him. Now, a big eagle is coming after him. Caridwin again.

09:49.280 --> 10:01.200
Merlin thinks. He moves here and there in the sky. But he can't lose.

10:02.160 --> 10:12.320
The eagle. Just then, Merlin sees a hunter far down in the forest.

10:14.000 --> 10:21.200
And there's a sudden noise. An arrow hits Caridwin.

10:21.520 --> 10:26.400
She falls to the ground near her house.

10:28.320 --> 10:33.600
More Fran runs to her dead body.

10:34.560 --> 10:39.440
Merlin, you demon. He cries angrily.

10:40.000 --> 10:43.520
One day, you must die for this.

10:51.920 --> 10:59.520
Chapter 5. King Vortigern's Castle

10:59.520 --> 11:23.920
After some years, Princess Adan, Merlin's mother, moves away to a convent.

11:24.000 --> 11:35.680
But Merlin stays in his father's castle. He reads books and works on his magic powers.

11:37.360 --> 11:42.720
I want to be the best magician in the kingdom, he says.

11:42.720 --> 11:49.440
At first, Merlin learns to change the weather.

11:51.360 --> 12:01.200
Next, he learns to see through walls. Then, he learns to look into the future.

12:01.840 --> 12:08.480
More Fran lives with his father in the forest.

12:08.480 --> 12:12.640
He often thinks about Merlin.

12:12.640 --> 12:18.480
Perhaps I can kill him with one of my mother's old potions.

12:18.480 --> 12:23.920
More Fran tells his friend, R. Well.

12:23.920 --> 12:32.400
But the old potion bottles have nothing in them.

12:34.080 --> 12:35.840
All but one.

12:37.520 --> 12:42.960
And this potion doesn't kill people. More Fran says.

12:43.840 --> 12:51.120
It makes ill people well again. So give it to somebody important.

12:51.920 --> 12:57.200
R. Well, answers. And pretend to be a magician.

12:59.600 --> 13:07.840
Soon after that, King Vortigern visits Wales after years of fighting.

13:09.440 --> 13:16.560
He has a new wife, Ronwen. But she is ill.

13:16.880 --> 13:20.960
More Fran hears about this.

13:20.960 --> 13:27.360
He goes to the king's men with the magic potion.

13:27.360 --> 13:33.760
Ronwen is well again after she drinks it.

13:33.760 --> 13:38.720
So Vortigern calls for more Fran.

13:38.720 --> 13:42.480
You can be my magician.

13:43.440 --> 13:44.640
The king says.

13:47.200 --> 13:53.120
Ronwen is happy in Wales. She wants to stay there.

13:54.640 --> 14:00.480
Let's make a castle on this hill. She tells Vortigern.

14:03.280 --> 14:06.800
Vortigern begins the new castle.

14:07.760 --> 14:14.080
But the walls fall down again and again.

14:17.680 --> 14:22.640
Make a magic potion and stop this.

14:22.640 --> 14:25.680
The king tells more Fran.

14:25.680 --> 14:31.760
I need the blood of a boy without a father for that.

14:31.760 --> 14:34.160
More Fran answers.

14:35.040 --> 14:39.920
Now, the son of a demon lives near here.

14:39.920 --> 14:45.280
Give me some men and I can bring him to you.

14:55.360 --> 15:00.400
Chapter 6. A true magician.

15:04.160 --> 15:24.480
Vortigern's men bring Merlin to the hill.

15:24.480 --> 15:27.200
Here's the demon's son.

15:27.200 --> 15:30.720
More Fran tells Vortigern.

15:30.720 --> 15:37.360
Kill him. I can make a potion with his blood and put it on the ground.

15:38.240 --> 15:41.200
Then you can finish your castle.

15:43.280 --> 15:47.280
More Fran's my enemy and he's wrong.

15:48.160 --> 15:49.440
Merlin cries.

15:50.480 --> 15:53.440
There are two dragons under the hill.

15:54.560 --> 15:57.040
I can see them through the ground.

15:58.080 --> 15:58.960
Dragons?

15:59.840 --> 16:01.520
Vortigern asks.

16:02.480 --> 16:04.960
Yes, Merlin cries.

16:05.680 --> 16:09.200
A red dragon and a white dragon.

16:10.240 --> 16:13.920
When they fight, the walls fall down.

16:16.080 --> 16:19.760
The dragons hear Merlin's cries.

16:20.960 --> 16:25.200
And they come up angrily through the ground.

16:29.680 --> 16:35.120
They are fighting and breathing fire and smoke.

16:36.560 --> 16:38.000
I can stop them.

16:39.040 --> 16:40.400
More Fran says.

16:42.240 --> 16:45.040
He pretends to do some magic.

16:46.480 --> 16:49.760
But he is not a true magician.

16:51.520 --> 16:57.760
The dragons breathe fire on more Fran and kill him.

16:59.760 --> 17:05.040
Merlin quickly changes the weather.

17:06.720 --> 17:12.480
Suddenly, there's a wall of rain in front of the dragons.

17:14.080 --> 17:16.960
They move up into the sky.

17:19.200 --> 17:24.480
When the rain goes, the dragons are far away.

17:24.800 --> 17:28.560
You're a true magician.

17:28.560 --> 17:30.560
Vortigern cries.

17:31.760 --> 17:36.880
He finishes his castle and calls for Merlin.

17:38.080 --> 17:41.040
Tell me about the future.

17:41.680 --> 17:43.200
The king says.

17:45.280 --> 17:48.400
Merlin closes his eyes.

17:49.680 --> 17:53.520
You don't have to worry about the future.

17:54.800 --> 17:58.160
Vortigern die without any children.

17:59.280 --> 18:00.240
He answers.

18:01.360 --> 18:04.560
Dark years of fighting come after that.

18:06.080 --> 18:10.400
Then I see a sword with magic light in it.

18:11.680 --> 18:17.520
A king with a wonderful castle and his beautiful wife.

18:19.120 --> 18:21.280
I'm that king's magician.

18:22.240 --> 18:24.240
Be my magician.

18:25.280 --> 18:27.280
Vortigern cries.

18:28.240 --> 18:29.040
No.

18:30.000 --> 18:31.440
Merlin answers.

18:32.240 --> 18:35.040
I must work more on my magic.

18:36.000 --> 18:41.600
I must be ready when my king and my country need me.

18:42.880 --> 18:47.520
Then Merlin changes into a hair.

18:47.520 --> 18:52.400
And runs away into the forest.

